rend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481820607"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "部队亲自答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImLi+/6GxidxSEAMaCDY5MzUyOTczILq7jIkGMGg4nA5AAnIJNDgxODIwNjA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1629788546.8600733", "card_id": "Q_481819418", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 352}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "北大姚洋称「企业捐款那么多不如取消 996，给骑手缴社保」，企业捐款和提高员工待遇应该如何做选择？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "北京大学国家发展研究院院长姚洋在接受采访时表示，企业与其拿出那么多钱来捐款，还不如不要搞「996」，让员工周末可以休息，给外卖骑手们都缴上社保，是不是更好？企业也不要再用算法和系统去算计那些骑手，他们跑得越来越快，骑手累，整个社会都累——骑手们横冲直撞，交规在他们眼里根本就不存在，这对于整个社会氛围的恶化，不是仅仅靠捐赠就能换来。企业的社会责任其实比捐款要重要得多。北大姚洋：企业捐款那么多不如取消 996 让员工周末可以休息"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4eb2e4540fbea225b45ec68ae757a7bd_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1574 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481819418"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImLi+/6GxidxSEAMaCDY5MzUyNzEyIPS4jIkGMDI4xQhAA3IJNDgxODE5NDE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1629788546.860731", "card_id": "Q_49922975", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 5069}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些外行看上去很高大上，但在内行眼里陋（low）得不行的东西？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有哪些「看似很 LOW，实则惊艳」的产品？镜像问题：有哪些外行看起来很 low，但是内行人却绝对很高大上的东西？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0298b39578912b19097e4d9da49c693d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1562 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/49922975"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImLi+/6GxidxSEAMaCDEyMTg1ODY1IJfO770FMHY4kNoGQARyCDQ5OTIyOTc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1629788546.8612456", "card_id": "Q_481584910", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 488}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待浙江理工大学一硕士研究生发了《Nature》选择回老家当公务员？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日发生的一件事，震动学术界。作为一所「双非」院校，8 月 18 日，浙江理工大学第 1 次以第一作者单位 / 通讯作者单位，将文章发表在 Nature 上，文章第一作者 Zhiwei Hao 是该校硕士研究生。 发 Nature 意味着什么? 博士保底，很多地方都能直升副教授甚至教授了，硕士发 Nature 可以说是前途无量。然而，正当人们感叹一颗学术新星冉冉升起时，却得知了一个惊人的消息：该学生硕士毕业后，马上回家考了公务员。 据网上流传的一张朋友圈截图，自称是 Zhiwei Hao 高中同学的人提到此事时，下方有人评论，他已经硕士毕业回到家宿州准备入职公务员了。 浙江理工大学硕士一作发 Nature，毕业后竟回家当公务员材料科学网：浙江理工大学，首篇第一单位《Nature》诞生！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-5f7d8d108c5ab8096f2751d80ffca678_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "838 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481584910"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImLi+/6GxidxSEAMaCDY5MzAwNTA1INHHhokGMEU49xtABXIJNDgxNTg0OTEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1629788546.8618605", "card_id": "Q_481172904", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 191}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《扫黑风暴》里公务员都有一个手提包，现实中也有吗？是国家发的还是自己买的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ccbe8a3caf5b18760931355a8eeb1a1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "685 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481172904"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "知乎评分 8.8", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImLi+/6GxidxSEAMaCDY5MjA4OTQxILWG/YgGMAw4vAdABnIJNDgxMTcyOTA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1629788546.8624341", "card_id": "Q_481042560", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 521}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待长沙检察院对货拉拉司机周某春以「涉嫌过失致人死亡」向法院提起公诉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "事情后续会如何发展？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e4eade5791d6d76ea4088c896